dc_title_s: Public Drainage Systems Hydrography, Faribault County: Minnesota
dc_description_s: This Feature Dataset contains those public drainage system (as defined by Minnesota Statute 103E) layers in Faribault County, Minnesota that are considered hydrographic: ditch/tile centerlines, elevation profile points, drainage structures as well as watersheds for ditch/tile systems (ditchsheds). Please note that separate metadata is available for each of these layers.
dc_creator_sm: Brandee Douglas, Faribault County SWCD, Asst Program Administrator
